reviewText: The Girls Gone Wild - Wildest Sex Ever 2 is not worth the $20 dollars I gave for it! There is little to no sex & a lot of kissing! They should have called it Girls Gone Wild - kiss fest! The length of the DVD is around 1 hour! I seen wilder things on TV then this DVD has on it, you be better off ordering 50 Shades of Gray! Gave it 2 out of 5 stars because the title of the DVD is misleading but the girls on the DVD where beautiful!
Too short for my taste, but like it anyway
This some of the hottest women you will ever see.

This was ok. The worst part about this dvd was all the scenes with the hot girls are very short and don't show really anything but all the parts with ok looking girls are long and the girls only do a few things with eachother

This is another one of those that looked like a half hearted release. Nothing much to justify the title of this thing as seems the case more often than not these days. If they are looking to lose thewir audience, they will do so with offerings such as this.
